### ========================================
### 34 - Feature Flags
### List, Update, Delete
### ========================================

### ----------------------------------------
### LIST FEATURE FLAGS
### ----------------------------------------

### Get all feature flags
GET {{baseUrl}}/feature-flags
Authorization: Bearer {{superAdminToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Get feature flag by name
GET {{baseUrl}}/feature-flags/MATERNAL_CARE_MODULE
Authorization: Bearer {{superAdminToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Get feature flags by scope
GET {{baseUrl}}/feature-flags?scope=HOSPITAL&scopeId={{hospitalId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{superAdminToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------
### MANAGE FEATURE FLAGS
### ----------------------------------------

### Create feature flag
POST {{baseUrl}}/feature-flags
Authorization: Bearer {{superAdminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "TELEHEALTH_ENABLED",
  "description": "Enable telehealth video consultation feature",
  "enabled": false,
  "scope": "PLATFORM",
  "metadata": {
    "maxParticipants": 2,
    "recordingEnabled": false,
    "provider": "zoom"
  }
}

### Update feature flag
PUT {{baseUrl}}/feature-flags/TELEHEALTH_ENABLED
Authorization: Bearer {{superAdminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "enabled": true,
  "description": "Telehealth video consultation - now enabled",
  "metadata": {
    "maxParticipants": 4,
    "recordingEnabled": true,
    "provider": "zoom"
  }
}

### Toggle feature flag
PUT {{baseUrl}}/feature-flags/TELEHEALTH_ENABLED/toggle
Authorization: Bearer {{superAdminToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Delete feature flag
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/feature-flags/TELEHEALTH_ENABLED
Authorization: Bearer {{superAdminToken}}
Accept: application/json
